item.title: CVE-2023-0170|2023-02-06T19:59:34.552Z -- unknown -- html5%20audio%20player
item.description: The Html5 Audio Player WordPress plugin before 2.1.12 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
